\c 34
\s Mozisi anokwirazve mugomo
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Zvivezere mahwendefa maviri emabwe akafanana neekutanga\x + Det. 10.1.\x*; ndigonyora pamahwendefa mashoko aiva ari pamahwendefa ekutanga\x + 34.28. Det. 10.2,4.\x* awaputsa\x + 32.19.\x*.
\v 2 Uye ugadzirire mangwanani, ugokwira mugomo reSinai mangwanani, ugomira pamberi pangu ipapo pamusoro pegomo\x + 19.20.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino kusakwira munhu newe\x + 19.12,13,21.\x*, uye kusava nemunhu anoonekwa pagomo rose; uye makwai nemombe zvisafura pamberi pegomo iri.
\p
\v 4 Zvino wakaveza mahwendefa maviri akafanana neekutanga, Mozisi ndokumuka mangwanani-ngwanani ndokukwira mugomo reSinai, Jehovha sezvaaiva amuraira, ndokutora mahwendefa maviri emabwe muruoko rwake.
\v 5 Jehovha ndokuburuka ari mugore, ndokuzvimisapo naye, ndokudana kuzita raJehovha\x + 33.19.\x*.
\v 6 Jehovha ndokupfuura pamberi pake, ndokudanidzira, \add achiti\add*: Jehovha, Jehovha Mwari, ane nyasha\x + Num.. 14.18. 2 Makor. 30.9. Neh. 9.17. Map. 86.15. 103.8. 111.4. 112.4. 116.5. 145.8. Jow. 2.13.\x* netsitsi, anononoka kutsamwa\x + 22.27.\x*, ane tsitsi zhinji nechokwadi\x + Map. 57.10. 108.4.\x*,
\v 7 achichengetera ngoni vane zvuru\x + 20.5,6. Det. 5.9,10. Jer. 32.18. Dhan. 9.4,9. Map. 103.3. 130.4. 1 Joh. 1.9.\x*, achikanganwira kuipa nekudarika nechivi, asi asingashaisisi mhosva \add ane mhosva\add*\x + Nah. 1.3; Eki. 23.21. Josh. 24.19. Job. 10.14.\x*, achitsiva kuipa kwemadzibaba pavana, uye pavana vevana, kusvika \add kuzera\add* rechitatu nerechina.
\v 8 Mozisi ndokukurumidza, ndokukotamira pasi, ndokunamata\x + 4.31;12.27.\x*.
\v 9 Zvino wakati: Kana ndakawana hangu nyasha pameso enyu, Ishe wangu, Ishe wangu ngaafambe hake pakati pedu\x + 33.15,16.\x*, nokuti rudzi rwemitsipa mikukutu\x + 32.9.\x*; mukanganwirewo kuipa kwedu nechivi chedu, mutitore kuva nhaka\x + Zek. 2.12. Det. 32.9. Map. 28.9. 33.12. 78.62. 94.14. Jer. 10.16.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Zvino wakati: Tarira, ndinoita sungano; pamberi pevanhu vako vose\x + 34.27. Det. 5.2; 29.14.\x* ndichaita zvishamiso zvisina kumbosikwa panyika yose, kana kundudzi dzese\x + Map. 77.14; 78.12. Det. 4.32. 2 Zvak. 7.23. Map. 147.20.\x*; nevanhu vose vauri pakati pavo vachaona basa raJehovha, nokuti chinhu chinotyisa chandichaita newe\x + Det. 10.21. Map. 145.6. Isa. 64.3.\x*.
\v 11 Uzvichengetedzere zvandinokuraira zuva rino\x + Det. 5.32. 6.3,25. 12.28,32. 28.1.\x*. Tarira, ndinodzinga kubva pamberi pako VaAmori, neVaKenani, neVaHiti, neVaPerezi, neVaHivhi, neVaJebhusi\x + 13.5.\x*.
\v 12 Uzvichenjerere zvimwe ungaita sungano nevagari venyika maunoenda\x + 23.32. Det. 7.2. Vato. 2. 2.\x*, zvimwe uve musungo pakati pako\x + 23.33.\x*.
\v 13 Asi muchaputsa aritari dzavo, nekuputsanya shongwe dzavo dzezvifananidzo\x + Det. 7.5. 12.3. Vato. 2.2.\x*, nekutema matanda avo ekunamata nawo\x + Det. 7.5. Vato. 6.25,26. 2 Madz. 18.4. 23.14. 2 Makor. 31.1. 34.3,4.\x*;
\v 14 nokuti haunganamati umwe mwari\x + 20.3,5.\x*, nokuti Jehovha zita rake rinova Godo\x + Isa. 9.6. 57.15.\x*, ndiMwari ane godo\x + 20.5.\x*;
\v 15 zvimwe ungaita sungano nevagari venyika\x + 34.12.\x*, uye vachipata vachitevera vamwari vavo\x + Rev. 17.7; 20.5. Det. 31.16. Vato. 2.17. Jer. 3.9. Eze. 6.9.\x*, uye vachibaira kuna vamwari vavo, nekukudana\x + Num.. 25.2. 1 VaKori. 10.27.\x* ugodya pachibairo chavo\x + Map. 106.28. 1 VaKori. 8.4,7,10.\x*;
\v 16 ukatorera vanakomana vako pavakunda vavo\x + Det. 7.3,4. 1 Madz. 11.2. Ezi. 9.2. Neh. 13.25.\x*; kana vakunda vavo vachifeva vachitevera vamwari vavo\x + Num.. 25.1,2. 1 Madz. 11.4.\x*, vachifevesa vanakomana vako vachitevera vamwari vavo.
\p
\v 17 Usazviitira vamwari vakaumbwa nekunyungudusa\x + 32.4,8. Rev. 19.4. Det. 27.15.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Mutambo wezvingwa zvisina kuviriswa\x + 12.15. 23.15.\x* uchauchengetedza. Mazuva manomwe uchadya zvingwa zvisina kuviriswa sezvandakakuraira panguva yakatarwa yemwedzi waAbhibhi\x + 12.2. 13.4.\x*, nokuti mumwedzi waAbhibhi wakabuda kubva muEgipita.
\p
\v 19 Chose chinozarura chizvaro ndechangu\x + 13.2,12,13. 22.29. Det. 15.19. Eze. 44.30.\x*, nedangwe rimwe nerimwe pachipfuwo chikono, nzombe nemakwai.
\v 20 Asi dangwe rembongoro\x + 13.13. Num.. 18.15.\x* ucharidzikunura negwayana; kanawo usingaridzikunuri, zvino uchavhuna mutsipa waro. Dangwe rimwe nerimwe revanakomana vako ucharidzikunura. Kusava neanoonekwa pamberi pangu asina chinhu\x + 23.15.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Mazuva matanhatu uchabata\x + 20.9.\x*, asi zuva rechinomwe uchazorora; nenguva yekurima nepakukohwa uchazorora.
\p
\v 22 Zvino uchachengetedza mutambo wemavhiki\x + 23.16. Det. 16.10,13.\x*, zvibereko zvitsva zvegoho regorosi, nemutambo wekuunganidza pakudzoka kwegore.
\p
\v 23 Katatu mugore\x + 23.14,17. Det. 16.16.\x* vanhurume vako vose vachaonekwa pamberi paShe Jehovha, Mwari waIsraeri.
\v 24 Nokuti ndichadzinga ndudzi pamberi pako\x + 15.9; Det. 4.38. Det. 7.1. Map. 78.55. 80.8.\x*, ndigokurisa miganhu yako\x + Det. 12.20; 19.8.\x*; uye hakuna munhu achachiva nyika yako\x + Zvir. 16.7.\x* pakukwira kwako katatu pagore kunoonekwa pamberi paJehovha, Mwari wako.
\p
\v 25 Usapa ropa rechibairo changu pamwe nechakaviriswa\x + 23.18.\x*; uye chibairo chemutambo wepasika chisasara kusvika mangwanani\x + 12.10.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Zvakanakisisa zvezvibereko zvekutanga zvemunda wako\x + 23.19.\x* uchazviunza kuimba yaJehovha Mwari wako. Usabika mbudzana mumukaka wamai vayo\x + 23.19. Det. 14.21.\x*.
\p
\v 27 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Zvinyorere mashoko awa, nokuti ndaita sungano newe naIsraeri\x + 34.10.\x* sezvinoreva mashoko iwawa.
\v 28 Zvino wakavapo naJehovha mazuva makumi mana neusiku makumi mana\x + 24.18. Det. 9.9,18.\x*; haana kudya chingwa, haana kunwa mvura. Zvino wakanyora pamahwendefa mashoko esungano, mirairo gumi\x + 34.1. Det. 10.2,4.\x*.
\p
\v 29 Zvino zvakaitika Mozisi paaiburuka kubva mugomo reSinai, mahwendefa maviri echipupuriro\x + 32.15.\x* ari muruoko rwaMozisi, paaiburuka kubva mugomo, kuti Mozisi waiva asingazivi kuti ganda rechiso chake raiva richibwinya zvaaiva\x + 34.30,35. 2 VaKori. 3.7. Mat. 17.2.\x* ataura naye.
\v 30 Zvino Aroni nevana vosewo vaIsraeri vakati vachiona Mozisi, tarira, ganda rechiso chake rakabwinya; zvino vakatya kuswedera kwaari.
\v 31 Zvino Mozisi wakavadana; uye Aroni nevatungamiriri vose veungano vakadzokera kwaari; Mozisi ndokutaura navo.
\v 32 Zvino shure kweizvozvo vana vaIsraeri vose vakaswedera; iye ndokuvaraira\x + 24.3.\x* zvose Jehovha zvaaiva amuudza pagomo reSinai.
\v 33 Zvino Mozisi apedza kutaura navo wakaisawo chifukidzo pachiso chake\x + 34.34,35. 2 VaKori. 3.13.\x*.
\v 34 Zvino pakupinda kwaMozisi pamberi paJehovha kutaura naye, waibvisa chifukidzo\x + 2 VaKori. 3.16.\x* kusvika abuda; zvino abuda wakataura kuvana vaIsraeri zvaarairwa.
\v 35 Zvino vana vaIsraeri vakaona chiso chaMozisi, kuti ganda rechiso chaMozisi raibwinya; Mozisi ndokudzosera chifukidzo pachiso chake, kusvika apinda kunotaura naye.